curam.util.client.model
Interface FieldBuilder

All Superinterfaces:
ComponentBuilder<Field>, java.io.Serializable
public interface FieldBuilder
extends ComponentBuilder<Field>

A builder for Field component objects. This interface supports the setting of the domain and binding paths for the field. Where paths are set from strings, the strings will be concatenated to form a path. The strings are considered to represent separate paths and steps, so the concatenation of, for example, "/hello" with "world", produces the path "/hello/world" and not "/helloworld".

When building fields, the ComponentBuilder.copy(Component, Object) method will not index the options and options alias paths of the bindings.
